quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  16,1,"Itegeko rya Allah (ryo kuza kw’imperuka) riregereje, bityo ntimuryihutishe. Ubutagatifu ni ubwe kandi nta ho ahuriye n’ibyo bamubangikanya na byo"
  16,2,"Ku bw’itegeko rye, (Allah) amanura malayika (Gaburiheli) azanye ubutumwa ku wo (Allah) ashaka mu bagaragu be (agira ati) “Muburire (abantu) ko nta yindi mana (ikwiye gusengwa by’ukuri) usibye Njye; bityo nimuntinye.”"
  16,3,Yaremye ibirere n’isi ku mpamvu z’ukuri. Ubutagatifu ni ubwe kandi nta ho ahuriye n’ibyo bamubangikanya na byo
  16,4,"Yaremye umuntu amukomoye mu ntanga, none uwo (muntu) yahisemo kuba umunyempaka ugaragara (mu guhakana izuka)"
  16,5,"(Allah) yanabaremeye amatungo; muri yo harimo ibibatera gususuruka (imyambaro) n’ibindi bibafitiye akamaro, ndetse hari n’ayo murya"
  16,6,Munashimishwa n’ubwiza bwayo igihe muyacyuye nimugoroba n’igihe muyahuye mu gitondo
  16,7,"(Ayo matungo) anikorera imitwaro yanyu iremereye akayijyana aho mutari gushobora kugera bitabagoye. Mu by’ukuri Nyagasani wanyu ni Nyirimpuhwe zihebuje, Nyirimbabazi"
  16,8,"(Yanaremye) ifarasi, icyimanyi (cy’ifarasi n’indogobe) ndetse n’indogobe; kugira ngo mubigendereho, kandi binababere imitako. Yanaremye n’ibindi mutazi"
  16,9,"Allah ni We werekana inzira igororotse (Isilamu), ariko hari n’izindi zigoramye. Kandi iyo aza kubishaka yari kubayobora mwese"